reviewText:
I thought this was great. Very educational....love this store. As a trainer, always looking to better my business and finding
so many great products in one place saves me time and money!!  HOOKED!
I have watched this before and am ordering again for a friend currently in Massage Therapy School, very educational!

I enjoyed the DVD as far as it went but I expected more "how-to" information. It was didn't go into types of stones to use or various modalities very much. You get to watch a session which I like but I did not walk away feeling like I knew much more than when I started.
